Re: Learn Japanese through MANGA
by becki_kanou » Sat 04.30.2011 8:21 pm The old Mangajin had some great tips on studying with manga, and they put out two books which are still available from amazon. MangajinI'd recommend getting a strong grasp of the basics before diving into manga though, otherwise you'll find it very frustrating.
そうだ、嬉しいんだ、生きる喜び！
例え胸の傷が痛んでも。
